  "texts": [
    "The suggested network achieved an accuracy of 93.50% on the colorectal histology dataset and 96.26% on the NCT-CRC-HE-100K dataset.",
    "With the combined dataset, the novel network achieved 99.21% accuracy.",
    "The ResNet architecture, along with an attention module, was employed in 26 to produce extensive feature maps to classify various tissues in HIs.",
    "Furthermore, neighborhood component analysis (NCA) effectively addresses the limitation of computational complexity.",
    "The selected features were inputted into an SVM classifier to train the model."
